rComments: Stephanie is such a caring and good prof! Her lectures were a little vague so the textbook is mandatory to cover all material. Test questions were very fair and reflected what was learned. Course consisted of a 40% midterm, 60% final, and the lab component of the course is a pass/fail course with weekly lab assignments. Overall, excellent prof!!

the powerpoints/voice overs were sometime very vague so read the book. every week you must submit lab homework, which is time consuming so don't leave it till last minute. Course consisted of midterm (40%) and a final (60%). Questions on both were very fair
